#
# TextFSM template: Cisco show arp
#
Value IP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value MAC ([0-9a-fA-F]+\.?[0-9a-fA-F]+\.?[0-9a-fA-F]+)
Value AGE (\d+|-)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)

Start
  ^Protocol\s+Address\s+Age\s+Hardware\s+Addr\s+Type\s+Interface -> Table

Table
  ^Internet\s+${IP}\s+${AGE}\s+${MAC}\s+\S+\s+${INTERFACE} -> Record
  ^.* -> Error
